Package: dtametaTMB
Title: Meta-Analysis of Diagnostic Test Accuracy Studies Using TMB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Claus", "Nowak", email = "claus.nowak@donau-uni.ac.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides functions to fit the hierarchical summary receiver
    operating characteristic (HSROC) model of Rutter and Gatsonis (2001),
    the bivariate binomial-normal model of Reitsma et al. (2005), and the
    bivariate time-to-event model of Hoyer et al. (2018) for multiple
    thresholds within studies using Template Model Builder.
